quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  28,61,"E ko on mo Men fodi fodaari moЖҙЖҙuri, ndi o hawrata e mu'un, wa'ata wa on mo Men dakmitiri dakamme nguurndam aduna, refti hara kanko on, Г‘alnde Darngal, ko e tawneteeЙ“e (ka Yiite) Й“en o jeyaa"
  28,62,"Г‘alnde O noddoyta Й“e, O wi'a: \"Ko honto kafidaaЙ—i am, Й—in Й—i aaЖҙoraynoЙ—on woni"
  28,63,"ЖҒen Й“e Konngol jojji e mu'un wi'a: \"Joomi amen, ko Й“ee woni ko men bewinnoo. Men bewinirno Й“e, wano men bewirnoo. Men daЙ—ndinike e MaaЙ—a. Wanaa menen Й“e rewaynoo"
  28,64,"[ЖҒe] wi'anee: \"Noddee non kafidaaЙ—i mon Й—in\". ЖҒe nodda Й—i, kono Й—i jaabotaako Й“e. ЖҒe yi'a lepte Й—en, (Й“e yeloo) sinno hara Й“e feewuno"
  28,65,"Г‘alnde O noddoyta Й“e, o wi'a: \"Ko honЙ—um jaabinoЙ—on NulaaЙ“e Й“en"
  28,66,"LamitorЙ—i Й—in wumiЙ—ana Й“e nden Гұalnde, Й“e lamndondirtaa"
  28,67,"Si ko tuubuЙ—o, o gomЙ—ini, o golli moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i, hino hasii ka o jeyee e malaaЙ“e Й“en"
  28,68,"Joomi maa no taga ko O muuyi, O suЙ“oo; suЙ“agol alanaa Й“e. Senaade woodanii Alla! O toowii e kon ko Й“e sirkata"
  28,69,"Joomi maa no anndi ko Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en suuЙ—ata, e kon ko Й“e feГұГұinta"
  28,70,"Ko Kanko Alla woni, Mo reweteeЙ—o alaa, si wanaa Kanko. Ko Kanko yettoore woodani aduna e laakara. Hino woodani Mo Гұaawoore nden. Ko ka Makko rutteteЙ—on"
  28,71,"Maaku: \"Yeetee lam, Si Alla waЙ—iranii on jemma on, duumiiЙ—o haa Г‘alnde Darngal, ko reweteeЙ—o hommbo, tanaa Alla, addanta on ndayngu? E on nanataa"
  28,72,"Maaku: \"Yeetee lam, Si Alla waЙ—iranii on Гұalorma on, duumiiЙ—o haa Г‘alnde Darngal, ko reweteeЙ—o hommbo, tanaa Alla, addanta on jemma, mo deeЖҙoton e mun? E on yi'ataa"
  28,73,"Hino jeyaa e yurmeende Makko, O waЙ—iranii on jemma e Гұalorma; fii no deeЖҙiron e (jemma) on, e no Й—aЙ“Й“iron ( e Гұalorma on), Й“ural Makko, e no belajo'o yettiron [Mo]"
  28,74,"Г‘alnde O noddoyta Й“e, O wi'a: \"Ko honto kadidaaЙ—i(renndidiiЙ—i) am, Й—in Й—in aaЖҙoraynoЙ—on woni"
  28,75,"Men Й—oofi e kala mofte, seedotooЙ—o, Men wi'a: \"Addee hujjaajji mon Й—in\". ЖҒe anndi wonnde goonga kan, ko Alla woodani; ko Й“e fefindotonoo kon majjitora Й“e"